Interface ReplicatedSharedHashMap.EntryResolver<K,V>

  • Enclosing interface:
    ReplicatedSharedHashMap<K,V>

    public static interface ReplicatedSharedHashMap.EntryResolver<K,V>
    provides a key and value from NativeBytes, this can be used in conjunction with the modification iterator to get the key and value out of the NativeBytes
